de.ityx.mediatrix.api.interfaces

Interface IVariable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IBeanVariable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseVariable, CheckVariable, CommentVariable, HiddenListVariable, ListVariable, MultilineStringVariable, NumberVariable, StringVariable

    public interface IVariable
    Describes variables that are inserted into the text. The variables are defined in the text objects.
